{"tid":950180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人啲老母成日捕住你幾時瞓覺...","createTime":"2018-12-21T10:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T11:46:11.000Z","uid":100551,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"58ca35fecb04f7fa1a16fe2ce973200e9eccbd55","tid":950180,"uid":100551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:23:13.000Z","msg":"我唔知有冇巴C同我一樣情況...<br />\n阿媽日日都不定時起身睇我瞓咗覺未...<br />\n然後有時遲過2、3點未瞓比佢捉到就好似大不肖咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生嚿叉燒好過生我已經唔算嚴重...幾乎要斷絕母子關係...係差在未講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時重一鬧鬧幾日...<br />\n我懷疑我殺人放火也不過如此...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最神奇者莫過於佢喺房都見到我未瞓...<br />\n我老豆老母房同我房有少少距離~即使站在門口也不大看到對方的房門~<br />\n理論上我未閂燈啲光都唔會照到過去(莫講話我有時閂咗門...)<br />\n而老母係唔使落床唔使起身就望到我未瞓...<br />\n係咩特異功能...我聲都冇出...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 其實好少1點半後瞓~係一星期2-3次會睇書/練琴/打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先會過1點半<br />\n都盡量1點前瞓~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終夜瞓對身體唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffaaf518605a038c934670f86b108c6272482a37","tid":950180,"uid":82482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"所以人大咗要私人空間是真<br />\n<br />\n搬走自住的重要"},{"pid":"f45620476c81fb942b8828a398615d7e2a5fb0a2","tid":950180,"uid":116614,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"唔睇你瞓咗未點同你老竇搞嘢吖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df50dcef9b0fce267ccf41692e26c92a71f697ec","tid":950180,"uid":193490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"衰仔，自己都唔識得保重自己身體"},{"pid":"eceb898afaf2deb3913d29213cac6f4548670b77","tid":950180,"uid":100551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f45620476c81fb942b8828a398615d7e2a5fb0a2","tid":950180,"uid":116614,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"唔睇你瞓咗未點同你老竇搞嘢吖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:37:27.000Z","msg":"唔會囉...好多時我老豆番夜都係咁...<br />\n(其實我都有諗過)不過其實我試過捕番轉頭...係冇事發生...<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e8b075cea4378b9f39892e83ef47ccc4c70a9d","tid":950180,"uid":34243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> same here<br />\n我都唔撚明<br />\n自己想訓就訓架啦 又唔係日日"},{"pid":"378febaf64f3eb568dfd693fc769c1f938b234a6","tid":950180,"uid":100551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28e8b075cea4378b9f39892e83ef47ccc4c70a9d","tid":950180,"uid":34243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> same here<br />\n我都唔撚明<br />\n自己想訓就訓架啦 又唔係日日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"夜瞓係唔好~但都唔使日日(目及)到實啫...<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8521e2497cb19a6cffd47d633b41b15f6bcdcc","tid":950180,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"強加自己人身價值觀姐<br />\n華人做開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91243a9ec2bd5b9d220ddc7e8730546ddab7ce4d","tid":950180,"uid":3502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"樓主中2~4? 認真早d訓 會矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932e41ad9dbbeb4c903248d57d7b9b071810ee59","tid":950180,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T11:36:05.000Z","msg":"你幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c1b42aa676bf0d154370753e12edba5e5d9c21","tid":950180,"u